high_descs: Take a step forward, then turn right and walk up to the white table to the right of the oven.
Pick up the small butter knife that is behind the loaf of bread on the white table.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the kitchen sink.
Place the butter knife into the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean butter knife.
Turn around and begin walking forward, then hang a right and walk over to the white table, then turn right to face the small black shelving unit.
Put the clean butter knife on the top shelf of the black shelving unit in the front right corner.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean butter knife on the top shelf of the black shelving unit.

high_descs: Turn to the right to see the white table.
Pick up the knife from the front of the table.
Take the knife and turn around, then to the left to find the sink.
Place the knife in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the knife.
Carry the knife take a few steps to the left to find the small black table.
Place the knife on the table.
anns.task_desc: Rinse off a knife and place it on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the table with the loaf of bread on it.
Pick up the knife from behind the bread.
Turn around, then turn left to reach the sink.
Wash the knife in the sink, then pick it up.
Walk to the small black table to the left of the sink.
Place the knife on the front right of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed knife on a table.
